      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m currently a Google AI Resident in the Brain team in Montreal. My mentor is Laurent Dinh and we are working on generative models for unspervised object discovery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the past, I complited my master&#39;s at University of Amsterdam, where I worked with Rianne van den Berg (AMLAB) on priors for VAEs and semi-supervised learning, and wrote my thesis during an internship at Mila, where I worked with Devon Hjelm on fundamental principles in Representation Learning for Zero Shot Learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In my free time I practice yoga, acroyoga and read a lot.&lt;/p&gt;
